{"tid":748332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【疑似誤導】男士平均預期壽命係幾多？香港年金公司：86歲，政府統計處：81.3歲","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T04:41:13.000Z","uid":36901,"like":48,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9e15e413d435bca835b54dff2d1d2fc811d67a","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"香港年金公司執行董事兼總裁劉應彬Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n問題 3: 對一位 65 歲的長者來說，回本期太長，要成 15 年，香港男性的平均壽命只有「82」歲左右，賺得兩年就拜拜。（筆者註：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根據統計數據，65歲男士的預期壽命約為 86 歲</strong></span>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkmca.hk/files/small_banner/2/Is%20the%20Life%20Annuity%20Your%20Cup%20of%20Tea_20180716.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmca.hk%2Ffiles%2Fsmall_banner%2F2%2FIs%2520the%2520Life%2520Annuity%2520Your%2520Cup%2520of%2520Tea_20180716.pdf&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9df7db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkmca.hk/files/small_banner/2/Is%20the%20Life%20Annuity%20Your%20Cup%20of%20Tea_20180716.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n老劉︰「香港年金」是長期保險產品，它的特點是投保人愈長壽，回報率就愈高，所以投保人應著眼於它的長期回報而非短期回報。關於回本期，從保單每年仍有的價值看，理論上第 10 年就已回本，因這位 65 歲投保的男士到 75 歲時所支取的年金總額，再加上該年保單的價值，已超過他最初的保費。不過這個回本期的問題並不是重點，因為若你有興趣購買「香港年金」，應該是著眼它可給你的長遠保障，志不在回本﹗<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/press_release/pressReleaseDetail.jsp?charsetID=2&amp;pressRID=4200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fpress_release%2FpressReleaseDetail.jsp%3FcharsetID%3D2%26pressRID%3D4200&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c7878dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/press_release/pressReleaseDetail.jsp?charsetID=2&amp;pressRID=4200</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在二零一六年，男性的出生時平均預期壽命為81.3年</span></strong>，而女性則為87.3年。與其他經濟體比較，香港的死亡率正處於一個甚低的水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處明明寫81.3歲，年金公司居然可以話係86歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁是咪誤導先？有冇違犯商品說明條例??"},{"pid":"820ff66847bd492f626dead58baf4152d5da4fdf","tid":748332,"uid":60536,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"年金公司話自己做咗另一個統計係86歲都吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accdaf797781d64dc0b99d750bfe421be25f10c8","tid":748332,"uid":18568,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"有錢85<br />\n無錢25"},{"pid":"71a48981f9a566eded2b6f0873b81fa7b9151974","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"820ff66847bd492f626dead58baf4152d5da4fdf","tid":748332,"uid":60536,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"年金公司話自己做咗另一個統計係86歲都吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"我懷疑佢地自己內部9做左一個model出黎,但冇公開,然後通街同人講4厘，計政府個預計壽命只有1厘多d，唔會有人理佢<br />\n<br />\n年金公司話晒都係政府擁有，但d銷售宣傳手法卻極為誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4f5a6b9288b469d7782270dcc06d5d344a9d17","tid":748332,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c9921760291e3012e4ee18fb064932ac5044aa","tid":748332,"uid":60536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71a48981f9a566eded2b6f0873b81fa7b9151974","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"820ff66847bd492f626dead58baf4152d5da4fdf","tid":748332,"uid":60536,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"年金公司話自己做咗另一個統計係86歲都吹佢唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"我懷疑佢地自己內部9做左一個model出黎,但冇公開,然後通街同人講4厘，計政府個預計壽命只有1厘多d，唔會有人理佢<br />\n<br />\n年金公司話晒都係政府擁有，但d銷售宣傳手法卻極為誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"佢鳩up都得啦 個統計citation又冇 咩機構做又冇"},{"pid":"3cec0868de5c3108c6e8c775d62a1aec56b7fdbd","tid":748332,"uid":57410,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"大家計法唔同啫"},{"pid":"2066f48212d3d10846dd4e2be7f54c6a8fc4afb5","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"【政府年金】首日登記反應冷淡 長者：唔夠應付每月使費！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府年金首日登記反應冷淡<br />\n<br />\n政府的「終身年金計劃」首日接受長者登記，但反應一般，<span style=\"color: red;\">截止上午11時，只有6名長者前往旺角匯豐銀行遞交表格。</span><br />\n<br />\n七十歲以下的高先生認購了五十萬港元公共年金，他指選擇公共年金比私營年金、股票等其他投資「穩陣」，但認為每月發放年金金額不足夠應付每月花費，只視之為其中一項投資，他亦透露有另外作股票投資。<br />\n同為七十歲以下的一名女性長者表示有參與公營及私營年金計劃，但未有透露認購金額。她指「凡事無絕對保障」，不會以公共年金為單一投資，會另外作好準備。<br />\n另一名男性長者指已認購一百萬港元，為投保上限金額，但指每月發放的5800元不足應付日常開支，所以存有其他積蓄。不過，他認為公共年金計劃能夠保障生活，計劃之後會用餘下積蓄作更進取的投資。<br />\n記者：江子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d7a89038cc2233e45b0200e6a7567932bb9905","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"日本公布全球平均壽命　香港男女蟬聯長壽冠軍<br />\n<br />\n07月21日(六) 11:29<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼香港男女蟬聯長壽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n日本厚生勞動省周五（20日）發表2017年度全球平均壽命統計，香港再次成為全球男女最長壽的地區，女性平均壽命87.66歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">男性則為81.7歲</span>。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本女性位居第二，平均壽命為87.26歲，連續第3年排名第二，比2016年長壽了0.12歲。報道指她們在1985年至2010年間，一直高踞全球最長壽榜榜首，但在2011年因日本發生三一一大地震，而被香港追過；雖然曾在2012年回歸榜首，但到2015年再被香港超越。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報告指，日本男性雖然平均增加了0.11歲，但排名卻跌至第三位，平均有81.09歲，第二位的瑞士男性平均壽命是81.5歲。厚生勞動省官員表示：「各地人口愈趨長壽，相信與愈來愈多人關注健康有關，未來醫療技術進步，壽命可能會更長。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n厚勞省還計算了「健康壽命」，即是無需護理、並非臥床不起、可自立生活的人，2016年的女性為74.79歲，男性為72.14歲。當局認為，如何將平均壽命與健康壽命的差距縮小，成為關注重點。"},{"pid":"0656d527bdb988c5797b10b6eb1dd748f565bf36","tid":748332,"uid":37522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"唔知佢點計<br />\n<br />\n但係佢話65歲男士平均預期壽命86同埋香港男士平均壽命82冇抵觸。佢呢個計法應該係排除左d 0-64歲死既人。<br />\n<br />\n例如佢出個report話85歲男士平均預期壽命90歲，都冇話錯既"},{"pid":"bc0c4cff6a3df34044fc5a31e1073b816ff1b09a","tid":748332,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c9e15e413d435bca835b54dff2d1d2fc811d67a","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"香港年金公司執行董事兼總裁劉應彬Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n問題 3: 對一位 65 歲的長者來說，回本期太長，要成 15 年，香港男性的平均壽命只有「82」歲左右，賺得兩年就拜拜。（筆者註：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根據統計數據，65歲男士的預期壽命約為 86 歲</strong></span>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkmca.hk/files/small_banner/2/Is%20the%20Life%20Annuity%20Your%20Cup%20of%20Tea_20180716.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmca.hk%2Ffiles%2Fsmall_banner%2F2%2FIs%2520the%2520Life%2520Annuity%2520Your%2520Cup%2520of%2520Tea_20180716.pdf&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9df7db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkmca.hk/files/small_banner/2/Is%20the%20Life%20Annuity%20Your%20Cup%20of%20Tea_20180716.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n老劉︰「香港年金」是長期保險產品，它的特點是投保人愈長壽，回報率就愈高，所以投保人應著眼於它的長期回報而非短期回報。關於回本期，從保單每年仍有的價值看，理論上第 10 年就已回本，因這位 65 歲投保的男士到 75 歲時所支取的年金總額，再加上該年保單的價值，已超過他最初的保費。不過這個回本期的問題並不是重點，因為若你有興趣購買「香港年金」，應該是著眼它可給你的長遠保障，志不在回本﹗<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/press_release/pressReleaseDetail.jsp?charsetID=2&amp;pressRID=4200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fpress_release%2FpressReleaseDetail.jsp%3FcharsetID%3D2%26pressRID%3D4200&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c7878dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/press_release/pressReleaseDetail.jsp?charsetID=2&amp;pressRID=4200</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在二零一六年，男性的出生時平均預期壽命為81.3年</span></strong>，而女性則為87.3年。與其他經濟體比較，香港的死亡率正處於一個甚低的水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處明明寫81.3歲，年金公司居然可以話係86歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁是咪誤導先？有冇違犯商品說明條例??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"統計處用國際標準，即係所謂既生命樹<br />\n年金用65歲標準，65歲年死左果啲唔計<br />\n條平均數自然高左"},{"pid":"4a9abfa6b6f841780dab4ec574544d9614fb3c6f","tid":748332,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"65歲前死左"},{"pid":"f83f4abed2eab9b816028c61dbd07cf0d6fcc345","tid":748332,"uid":19055,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"班基金佬冇得賺既點會開個plan出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12d20d9890663727e32fb3a014fb97e48239fa7","tid":748332,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83f4abed2eab9b816028c61dbd07cf0d6fcc345","tid":748332,"uid":19055,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"班基金佬冇得賺既點會開個plan出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"賭長唔長命"},{"pid":"f6245c75d0e4c17fdfab31cbbb66184fae87c5ce","tid":748332,"uid":18944,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"過左65歲就平均86歲命"},{"pid":"6ed0e77eaa2291e96cf0821770e5d16777d2689e","tid":748332,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"又講到幾吸引 得果6條水魚"},{"pid":"b4c0cdc55e25f1467daf5c01e45c235639af9be8","tid":748332,"uid":90911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"86係condition佢65歲冇死<br />\n81.3 係就咁average"},{"pid":"916e63be370ed000cc6cade31fcf4e03db3a19fb","tid":748332,"uid":119895,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"上面班盲毛唔識conditional expectation<br />\n我當你e+ 90歲，咁你預期壽命會唔會得82？"},{"pid":"b1b686bda3618330e30c6c4a50c3cf89f6529b44","tid":748332,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"總之有殺冇賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dfe1925267836bbf137c363e48f2c6d4d6e8c7","tid":748332,"uid":17286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年乜鬼野金"},{"pid":"becea9e2c7c33099c735a227f6f75fe1837630c1","tid":748332,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"佢又唔講埋比有錢佬拉高平均值<br />\n窮人相對短命<br />\n而佢對象又係較窮既大眾<br />\n所以回報率真係未必咁高"},{"pid":"55ecb23c93621e681c0fe1d3eb3e5a63e6f9ec7d","tid":748332,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cec0868de5c3108c6e8c775d62a1aec56b7fdbd","tid":748332,"uid":57410,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"大家計法唔同啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"學日本有仔女為左老人福利金，就算個老人情況點都唔俾拔喉。由得佢係醫院。"},{"pid":"622ebc86b84635de0c3f0920751cf72c21276546","tid":748332,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"臨死都要為錢煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd46129a9ee8db9a603ff3a7385f62dea1267ac","tid":748332,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e538f7adda107cf1f390228b216c4ec884137f6d","tid":748332,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d7a89038cc2233e45b0200e6a7567932bb9905","tid":748332,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"日本公布全球平均壽命　香港男女蟬聯長壽冠軍<br />\n<br />\n07月21日(六) 11:29<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼香港男女蟬聯長壽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n日本厚生勞動省周五（20日）發表2017年度全球平均壽命統計，香港再次成為全球男女最長壽的地區，女性平均壽命87.66歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">男性則為81.7歲</span>。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本女性位居第二，平均壽命為87.26歲，連續第3年排名第二，比2016年長壽了0.12歲。報道指她們在1985年至2010年間，一直高踞全球最長壽榜榜首，但在2011年因日本發生三一一大地震，而被香港追過；雖然曾在2012年回歸榜首，但到2015年再被香港超越。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報告指，日本男性雖然平均增加了0.11歲，但排名卻跌至第三位，平均有81.09歲，第二位的瑞士男性平均壽命是81.5歲。厚生勞動省官員表示：「各地人口愈趨長壽，相信與愈來愈多人關注健康有關，未來醫療技術進步，壽命可能會更長。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n厚勞省還計算了「健康壽命」，即是無需護理、並非臥床不起、可自立生活的人，2016年的女性為74.79歲，男性為72.14歲。當局認為，如何將平均壽命與健康壽命的差距縮小，成為關注重點。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"日本剛水災死咗二百<br />\n香港出年又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}